IR and Raman intensities were calculated based on the methodology used in the literature as follows87,90.
Vibrational frequencies were computed using the ASE Vibrations class. Eigenmodes (ω) were determined based on the calculated Hessian matrix. A displacement of atoms of 0.01 Å was used throughout.
